name: RN apps: iOS ONLY - Last DM/GM in the list does not overlap with 2 dots

customFields.Priority P1 to P4: P4 - Low-Impact (Edge or unsuitable to repeat?)

inline.description:
RN apps (iOS ONLY) - last DM/GM in the list does not overlap with 2 dots
(There are no floating dots in Android)
--------------------
1. Scroll down in the channels list to the bottom of the screen
inline.expectedResult: Ensure that the 2 dots (used for swiping between team sidebar and channels list) do not overlap with the last DM/GM in the channels list. There should also be an overlay behind the dots.
